OL,4,CShops and schools proposed for council
OL,5,Celection pilots in Wales
OL,6, People could be allowed to vote in
OL,7, supermarkets or schools in some parts
OL,8, of Wales at next year's council
OL,9, elections.
OL,11,FNew "flexible voting" proposals could
OL,12,Fsee polling take place over multiple
OL,13,Fdays or a weekend before an election,
OL,14,Fin an effort to boost turnout.
OL,16,FThe Welsh government has asked if
OL,17,Fcouncils would like to pilot the ideas.
OL,19,FBut a body of electoral officials said
OL,20,Fthere was not a "huge" amount of time
OL,21,Fto implement the proposals.
